OL,6,FA bench has been erected on
OL,7,FWorcestershire estate in memory of a
OL,8,Fschoolboy who was killed by his
OL,9,Fparents.
OL,11,FAlfie Steele was nine-years-old when
OL,12,Fhe was "repeatedly assaulted, beaten"
OL,13,Fand "held" in a cold bath as
OL,14,Fpunishment by Carla Scott, 35, and
OL,15,FDirk Howell, 41 - both from Birmingham.
OL,17,FThe pair have been jailed for a total
OL,18,Fof almost 60 years.
