OL,6,FIn tribute to the young boy, Hindlip,
OL,7,FMartin Hussingtree & Salwarpe Parish
OL,8,FCouncil has created a bench, which can
OL,9,Fbe found on the Copcut Rise Estate in
OL,10,FDroitwich.
OL,12,F"To ensure Alfie's legacy is
OL,13,Feverlasting"
OL,15,FWychavon District Councillor Daniel
OL,16,FBirch said: "The bench has been
OL,17,Finstalled as part of the community's
OL,18,Faim to ensure Alfie's legacy is
OL,19,Feverlasting.
