OL,6,F"The hope is it serves as a stark
OL,7,Freminder of the horrific tragedy that
OL,8,Fwas Alfies death.
OL,10,F"The untimely death of Alfie Steele is
OL,11,Fa tragedy that as a society we should
OL,12,Fnever have to face and therefore its
OL,13,Fcrucial when these events do occur, we
OL,14,Fremember them and reflect.
OL,16,F"However, we also hope for those on
OL,17,FCopcut Rise and within the wider
OL,18,Fcommunity that knew Alfie the bench is
OL,19,Fa place for them to reflect on what a
OL,20,Fhappy and compassionate boy Alfie was.
